Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.90,0:00:06.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.03,0:00:09.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.49,0:00:16.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.91,0:00:19.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.95,0:00:21.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:25.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 結果還是沒找到…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.84,0:00:26.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我得去找她
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.96,0:00:29.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:34.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我有很重要的話對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.49,0:02:22.83,Default2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}鵝肝醬飯糰 魚翅飯糰 珠雞肉飯糰 松露飯糰\N魚子醬飯糰 鹹魚乾飯糰 榴槤飯糰 甜瓜飯糰 蕃茄豆湯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.26,0:02:25.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這個還有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:31.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:35.39,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 還有沒有蕃茄豆湯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:37.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.20,0:02:42.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我們已經不賣蕃茄豆湯了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.31,0:02:43.55,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:47.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,鬍子紳士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.23,0:02:48.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你… 你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:51.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫紗繪 佐倉紗繪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:53.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,之前給你看照片的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.25,0:02:58.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是你啊 你還有在便利商店打工啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.09,0:03:02.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,請問 你在找什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:03.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:15.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 那麼那個叫蒼乃的女孩是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:18.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:22.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以全部都是我引起的 懂了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:25.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 那麼那個叫依人的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.53,0:03:27.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 別放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:28.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:29.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,破爛兔拳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.72,0:03:33.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你在意也無濟於事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:36.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這個 飯還沒買回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:39.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒很想吃吃看鵝肝醬口味的飯糰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:42.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你總是這樣扯開話題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:46.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,當然也因為剛史的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:48.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你還不太信任我們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:53.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 我並不是不信任你們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.79,0:03:56.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不覺學會了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:03:58.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這種生活方式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:02.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為如果不這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:09.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,會很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:21.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你騙人吧 這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:24.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有騙人 拜託 相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:32.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,蕃茄豆湯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.79,0:04:34.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 蕃茄豆湯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:37.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,鬍子紳士來買的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:38.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:39.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,番茄…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:49.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:53.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為今天只上半天課
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.72,0:04:56.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你一個人過一整天會不會太寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:04:57.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:04:59.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我打擾到你了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:02.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼 不過 平底鍋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:06.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 我該怎麼做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.83,0:05:09.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這個時候應該採取的措施是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.80,0:05:13.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對… 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:14.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,給我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:17.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:22.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 用小火慢慢燉是竅門
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:25.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼你會來？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:30.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名沒說過不可以來這裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.56,0:05:37.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,要是這樣的話 蒼乃就變成一個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.55,0:05:44.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:48.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:51.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了 姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:55.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:57.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小依特製法國吐司
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:06:00.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然有一半是蒼乃做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:03.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 正好肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.18,0:06:04.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.27,0:06:06.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.14,0:06:09.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,味道如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:10.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:12.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:13.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼乃呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.64,0:06:15.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,普通
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:17.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:23.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,果然吃飯要像這樣與蒼乃和依人一起吃才是最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:24.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:24.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:27.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小依一直都自己做料理嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:29.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:36.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 這個問題由…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:37.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,石月 你來解答
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:40.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,石月？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:45.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 石月她身體有點不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:51.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,很溫柔的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:55.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,說是為了朋友來找蕃茄豆湯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:56.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,然後他往哪裡走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:01.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,他說有目標 找一會兒再回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:09.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:13.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,請允許我明早再來這裡拜訪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:14.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:18.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 祝你們姊弟度過一個舒適的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:35.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊也快點去吃吧 我來洗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.53,0:07:40.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:44.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我討厭你這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:46.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊？ 突然這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:50.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼回來？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:53.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是我和姊姊的家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:54.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,回來是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:56.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不要隱瞞了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:02.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼姊姊你也別隱瞞了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:06.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有隱瞞 什麼也沒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:07.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你在隱瞞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:12.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你見到茉莉了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.52,0:08:15.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有 但我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:17.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:22.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我刺傷了茉莉 姊姊想讓我堅信那是個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.89,0:08:23.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:28.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊 你認識茉莉吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.81,0:08:32.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊對我隱瞞了什麼 是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:34.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有隱瞞你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:39.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想和依人兩個人在一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.82,0:08:58.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,除此之外 我什麼都不要 什麼都不考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:08:59.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:01.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這有什麼錯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:04.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼依人要生氣？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.05,0:09:07.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,突然冒出來的是她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:09.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有什麼四方茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:11.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:14.15,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的吧 茉莉的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:15.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,毫無關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.57,0:09:17.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你什麼都不用知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:20.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我的弟弟 僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:22.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我會給你幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:24.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,用盡我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:27.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不管我變得多骯髒 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.67,0:09:28.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:32.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:35.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道的是真相
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:36.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:52.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼乃是夜禍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:06.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:13.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.54,0:10:25.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我平日積德吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:28.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡的那位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:35.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼… 男人都那麼遲鈍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:43.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡的鬍子眼鏡男 看這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.88,0:10:53.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就為了這種理由追我到這裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:56.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 因為無論如何都想見茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:10:57.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:02.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在一起的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:04.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:10.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,很遺憾 這個人不是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:12.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你別牽扯進來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:18.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 請幫我傳達一句話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:20.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,森宮依人現在很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.07,0:11:23.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:29.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我走在街上 偶然遇見她的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:31.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會幫你傳達的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:16.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我是小依的姊姊 叫石月真名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:18.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小依總是受您照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:21.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是真名？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.98,0:12:24.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,禦池學園
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:27.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 今天正好是開學典禮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:29.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:33.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,應該叫姊姊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.06,0:12:35.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:36.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.79,0:12:40.15,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:43.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫森宮依人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.05,0:12:49.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,0:12:53.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫真名 石月真名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.76,0:13:00.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:02.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:09.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小依實在隱瞞不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.79,0:13:11.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,還是老實說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.13,0:13:15.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,今天去蒼乃家了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.78,0:13:17.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.29,0:13:20.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒遵守約定 很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:23.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 依人也回到家了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:25.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,又像往常那樣快樂了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:25.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小依
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:27.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:30.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好久沒一起睡了 一起睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:35.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.33,0:14:08.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.02,0:14:14.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你一定會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:20.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我終於想起來了 這裡發生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.26,0:14:21.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.47,0:14:25.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 雖然只是一些片段 但還是想起了一些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.82,0:14:29.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,穿和服的茉莉 還有那個洞穴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:32.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:35.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊和茉莉很早以前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:39.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,也許早在幾百年以前就認識了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.88,0:14:41.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:43.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:44.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那我是什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:46.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,既不是夜禍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.36,0:14:50.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我卻有以前的茉莉和姊姊還有自己身影的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.58,0:14:53.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.93,0:14:58.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人在過去確實存在過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.66,0:15:02.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 任何人都只能活一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:04.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.52,0:15:07.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是在那時候就已經死掉的依人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.64,0:15:09.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼說我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:12.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.97,0:15:28.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,忍耐一下 這就是知道真相所要忍受的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.15,0:15:30.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,必須的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.23,0:15:31.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.32,0:15:34.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.94,0:15:48.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是你真正的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.43,0:15:52.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你真正的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:05.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:19.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.13,0:16:22.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.89,0:16:36.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.29,0:16:41.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人 依人 依人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:42.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:44.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要 我不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.46,0:16:46.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:52.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:55.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明是活祭品 卻還一直活著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:58.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊 茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.49,0:17:01.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,然後蒼乃就執迷於
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,0:17:03.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,重新製造你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.16,0:17:12.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就終於
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,0:17:25.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.30,0:17:29.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 蒼乃製造出來的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.26,0:17:32.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,植入了依人的記憶的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.35,0:17:34.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.73,0:18:13.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:17.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？ 還沒睡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.32,0:18:20.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,睡眠不足可是皮膚的天敵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:23.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣真的好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:27.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個叫依人的男孩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.49,0:18:30.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定就那麼崩潰了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.08,0:18:33.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:35.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,剛史
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:38.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可這也是沒辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.83,0:18:42.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是他本人想知道真相
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.40,0:18:47.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,選擇了活在不安 痛苦 和真實中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.98,0:18:49.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,誰也無法去阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.80,0:18:55.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不也一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.85,0:19:00.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,過來這邊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.24,0:19:39.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 依人是怎樣一個人啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.52,0:19:44.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,果然和現在的我一樣的性格嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.97,0:19:45.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,還有姊姊也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.09,0:19:46.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:49.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,都是以前的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.41,0:19:51.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,已經忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,0:19:54.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我記住的只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.53,0:19:57.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:02.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我什麼都不是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.34,0:20:06.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是依人 連人類也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:07.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只不過是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.68,0:20:08.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:11.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你什麼也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.47,0:20:16.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只是一個扮演過去的依人的可憐幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.04,0:20:19.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但也並不是沒有存在過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.56,0:20:20.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.22,0:20:33.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可以親吻 也可以握手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.54,0:20:36.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你確實在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.71,0:20:42.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然受著依人的記憶影響 但你自己也在思考
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:44.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,自己做著自己想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.89,0:20:50.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡這樣的你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.95,0:20:51.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:53.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.22,0:20:56.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:20:59.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:11.87,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.41,0:21:14.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,明明應該在的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.35,0:21:17.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那就沒辦法了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.24,0:21:19.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,要遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.67,0:21:20.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.10,0:21:25.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.52,0:21:28.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.93,0:21:38.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:41.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:43.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這把刀的使用方法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.22,0:23:35.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小依終於也學會手刀了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.89,0:23:37.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.98,0:23:41.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,請叫我小依小姐 真名
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.56,0:23:42.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,(><) x1
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.81,0:23:43.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,(><) x2
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.73,0:23:44.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,(><) x3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.03,0:02:20.03,FBT,NTP,0,0,360,,{\fad(480,480)\bord3\shad0\blur6}搖晃的幻境
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.43,0:23:45.44,FBT,NTP,560,0,224,,夢想之歌
